Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:27.20,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:322989,327202}The entrance exams for Fujimi High School are getting more difficult every year.{NOTE:富士見高校の入試は毎年難しくなっているから、しっかれやるより。}
