Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.66,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:328161,329663}– Yes sir.\N– Yes sir.{NOTE:—はい。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:32.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:329663,332582}Um, what is going on now in the volleyball club?{NOTE:あの、バレー部のほう今どうなっているんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:34.29,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:333375,334292}Hmm.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:39.58,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:334292,339589}The newcomers will be participating in\Na regional tournament on January 15th next year.{NOTE:県の新人戦が来年1月15日から始まることに急に決まったんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:42.46,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:339589,342467}January 15th? That's only two months from now.{NOTE:1月15日といえば後わずか2ヶ月ですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:44.92,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:343176,344928}Yes, you're right.{NOTE:ん、そうなんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:50.51,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:346054,350517}To tell you the truth, I'm busy arranging future plans for each student.{NOTE:ところが僕は会いに行くとみんなの進学や就職のことで忙しくて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:52.93,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:350517,352936}I don't have much time to appear on the court.{NOTE:…碌にコートにも顔を出せない状態でね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:57.31,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:354020,357315}I've asked Kashiwagi to take care of the club for now.{NOTE:だから今のどころ柏木一人にやってもらってるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:05:59.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:358275,359192}Oh…{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:01.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:359192,361903}Professor, I'll show up on the court as much as I can.{NOTE:先生。私もできるだけコートに出ます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:03.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:361903,363071}Me too.{NOTE:私もです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:05.57,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:363071,365574}But you have your studies.{NOTE:しかし君たちは勉強は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:07.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:365574,367075}We'll be fine.{NOTE:勉強なら大丈夫です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:11.83,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:367075,371830}I was planning to practice a little everyday anyway.{NOTE:どっち道体を慣らしてみて、毎日少しでもいいから練習しようと思ってたんですから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:18.00,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:371830,378003}Besides, if I don't play even for a day,\Nmy condition goes down and it affects my studies.{NOTE:それに私一日でもボールに触らないと調子が狂っちゃって帰って勉強の能率が悪くなるんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.50,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:379004,380505}I see. Thank you.{NOTE:あ、有難う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.59,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:381131,382591}That'll be really helpful.{NOTE:や、助かるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:25.17,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:382591,385176}But make sure you don't overdo it.{NOTE:しかし決して無理のないようにな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:25.84,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:385176,385844}– Yes sir.\N– Yes sir.{NOTE:—はい。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:35.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:390473,395812}When we graduate, the Fujimi Academy's volleyball club will be in your hands.{NOTE:私達が卒業したら、この富士見学園バレー部を支えていくのはあなたたちよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:38.10,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:395812,398106}Work hard for your first tournament!{NOTE:みんな新人戦目指して頑張ってね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.85,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:398106,399858}– Yeah!\N– Alright!{NOTE:—はい！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:44.90,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:399858,404905}We have to study for the entrance exams,\Nso we might not have much time.{NOTE:私達これから受験勉強もしなきゃいけないし、あんまり時間はないかもしれないけれど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:48.11,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:404905,408116}But we'll practice with you as much as possible.{NOTE:でもできるだけみんなと一緒に練習するつもりよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:49.24,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:408116,409242}We're looking forward to it.{NOTE:よろしくね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.66,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:409242,410660}– Thank you.\N– Thank you.{NOTE:—お願いします！\\N—お願いします！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:55.87,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:410660,415874}I think entrance exams are a pain in the butt,\Nso I don't plan to go to high school.{NOTE:私は受験勉強なんて面倒くさいこと性に合わないから進学するのをやめたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:56.87,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:415874,416875}That's why…{NOTE:だから…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:58.33,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:416875,418335}Haha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.33,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:418335,419336}{\i1}That's{\i0} why…{NOTE:ダカラ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:01.25,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:419336,421254}…I'll take care of you full-time until graduation.{NOTE:卒業までばっちりやるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:05.00,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:421254,425008}With Captain and Midori,\Nthe tournament should be a breeze.{NOTE:新人戦はもちろんのことみんなキャプテンやみどりのように。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:08.01,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:425008,428011}I want you to work hard and aim for All-Japan.{NOTE:兎に角オールジャパンを目指して頑張って欲しいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.30,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:428011,429304}Do you hear?{NOTE:分かってるわね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.18,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:429304,430180}– Yes!\N– Yes ma'am!{NOTE:—はい！\\N—はぁい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:12.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:430180,432057}Then let's get started.{NOTE:それじゃ早速練習開始。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:13.01,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:432057,433016}Assume positions!{NOTE:位置について！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:13.97,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:433016,433975}– Okay!\N– Yeah!{NOTE:—はい！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:17.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:436478,437354}Here goes!{NOTE:行くわよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:29.49,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:448657,449491}Attack!{NOTE:アタック！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:45.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:465090,465757}Next!{NOTE:次！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:55.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:474557,475266}Come on!{NOTE:ほら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.26,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:477477,478269}One more!{NOTE:もう一本！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:07.90,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:484609,487904}Today I have to start studying for entrance exams.{NOTE:今日から私もいよいよ受験勉強に取りかかれなくっちゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:11.32,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:489197,491324}Okay. Now that it came down to it, let's do this!{NOTE:よし、やるとなったらやるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:494077,495578}I'm home.{NOTE:ただいま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:16.20,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:495578,496204}Oh?{NOTE:あら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:18.62,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:497455,498623}Huh…{NOTE:ま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.41,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:498623,500417}Who could it be?{NOTE:お客様かしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:22.25,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:500417,502252}Oh, welcome back.{NOTE:あ、お帰りなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:23.54,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:502252,503545}Who's here?{NOTE:あ。どなた？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:25.71,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:503545,505714}Kozue-chan, you have guests.{NOTE:お客様ですよ。こずえちゃんの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:27.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:505714,507298}Huh? I do?{NOTE:え？私に？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:29.50,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:507298,509509}Kozue-san, we've been waiting for you.{NOTE:あ、こずえさん、お待ちしておりました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:32.38,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:509509,512387}I'm a manager of the volleyball club for Mt. Tateyama Manufacturing.{NOTE:私立山製作所のバレー部のマネージャーです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:34.26,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:512387,514264}I'm from Black Pine Ironworks.{NOTE:私はXXXとのもんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:36.80,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:515390,516808}I represent Marunichi Textiles.{NOTE:私は丸日紡績のものです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:42.93,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:518977,522939}Kozue, these people came to recruit you for their company teams.{NOTE:こずえ。この方達はお前をスカウトにいらしたんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:43.98,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:522939,523982}Recruit?{NOTE:スカウト？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:48.23,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:525650,528236}Please come to Marunichi Textiles volleyball club.{NOTE:是非我が丸日紡績のバレー部へ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:50.98,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:528236,530989}No, please come to Shimizu Yamato.{NOTE:いいえ、是非是非清水大和へ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:55.41,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:530989,535410}Joining our Tateyama Manufacturing would be a tremendous leap forward.{NOTE:いいえ、是非躍進著しい地元の立山製作所のバレー部で。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:57.12,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:535410,537120}Besides, we're in the area.{NOTE:え、何といっても地元よね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:09:00.58,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:537120,540582}We can satisfy whatever needs you have regarding the contract money.{NOTE:契約金はできるだけそちらのご要望にお答えしますから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:03.16,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:540582,543168}So it's best for you to join Shimizu Yamato.{NOTE:なにどぞ我が清水大和へ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:06.08,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:543168,546087}No, as far as the contract money goes, our company—{NOTE:いいえ、契約金のことでしたら我が社の方が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:11.50,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:546087,551509}Our club offers not only good money, but you also get to train under the famous coach Ōshima.{NOTE:契約金もさることながら我がバレー部に入れば有名な大島監督の向上を受けられますよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:14.80,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:551509,554804}We'll quite literally make you into Japan's best player.{NOTE:文字通り日本一のプレイヤーになること請け合いです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.59,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:554804,557599}Please join our Black Pine Ironworks.{NOTE:是非XXXでお出でください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:21.47,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:557599,561478}If you play for our team, you will certainly participate in the next Olympic Games.{NOTE:家へ来たってオリンピック級のプレイヤーになること間違いなし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:23.73,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:562437,563730}Papa.{NOTE:パパ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:25.27,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:563730,565273}Okay, okay.{NOTE:はは、よしよし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:29.02,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:566441,569027}Gentlemen, I'd like to ask you not to speak all at the same time.{NOTE:皆さん。そう一気にXX出られたんでは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:34.74,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:570487,574741}I don't think I should interfere with my daughter's affairs as she's no longer a child.{NOTE:娘のことについては私は余計な差し出口をしない方針だんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:37.49,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:574741,577494}I respect her will.{NOTE:私は娘の意思を尊重します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:42.74,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:577494,582749}So, I'll let you meet with Kozue personally and discuss matter directly with her.{NOTE:ですからこの話も一応皆さんから直接こずえに話していただこうと思ったんですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:46.08,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:582749,586086}We really appreciate it.{NOTE:その点私どもも大変感謝しております。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:50.67,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:586086,590673}However, it seems all of this was\Na bit too surprising for my daughter.{NOTE:しかしあまりにも突然のことなので娘も非常にびっくりしてるようです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:52.50,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:590673,592509}You're perfectly right.{NOTE:それはおっしゃる通りですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:55.63,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:592509,595637}Let's present our offers to her one by one then.{NOTE:では一人ずつゆっくり説明することにいたしまして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:59.14,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:595637,599140}Gentlemen, I know it's sudden, but could\NI kindly ask you to just withdraw for today?{NOTE:あ、せっかくですが、今日のところは皆さんお引き取り下さい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:00.68,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:599140,600683}– Huh?\N– Eh?{NOTE:—え？\\N—え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:04.47,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:600683,604479}This is my request to you as Kozue's parent.{NOTE:俺はこずえの保護者である私からお願いすることなんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:06.39,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:604479,606397}It's a selfish request, but please withdraw for today.{NOTE:勝手ですがどうぞお引き取りよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.52,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:606397,608525}Such a pity…{NOTE:残念ですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:18.36,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:616533,618368}I was really surprised.{NOTE:本当に驚きましたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:23.45,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:618368,623456}I know you're the world's second, but to scout out such a small child…{NOTE:いくら世界で二位になったからって、こんな小さな子供にまでスカウトの手が伸びるなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:26.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:623456,626751}A small child? I'll be a high school student soon.{NOTE:あ、失礼ね。私はもうすぐ高校生よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:28.25,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:626751,628253}– Hahaha.\N– Oops.{NOTE:—ははは。\\N—あら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:33.17,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:628253,633174}You see, no matter how much a child grows up,\Nparents will always view them as little.{NOTE:親というものはね、いくら大きくなっても自分の子供が小さく見えるもんなんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:38.09,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:633174,638096}But who would've thought I'd get contacted by the famous Black Pine Ironworks or Shimizu Yamato…{NOTE:でも女子バレー界の名門のXXXやXXXからスカウトに来るなんて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:42.14,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:638096,642142}They must think a lot of me.\NThey offered contract money and everything.{NOTE:然も契約金までよ。よっぽど私の力をかってくれたのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:43.81,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:642600,643810}Hm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:45.18,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:643810,645186}– You urchin.\N– Hehe.{NOTE:—こいつ。\\N—えへへ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:49.39,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:645186,649399}But I think Kozue's success in the United States\Ndoes justify her confidence.{NOTE:しかし、アメリカでのこずえの活躍はそのぐらい自惚れる価値があるかもしれんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:52.06,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:649399,652068}– You too, Honey?\N– Hahaha.{NOTE:—あなたまでそんなことを？\\N—ははは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:53.65,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:652068,653653}It was just a joke.{NOTE:今の冗談だよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:653653,655780}Maybe I will let them recruit me?{NOTE:私スカウトされちゃうかな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:57.49,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:656364,657490}Hm?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.61,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:657490,658616}Kozue?{NOTE:こずえ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:10:59.40,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:658616,659409}Tee-hee.{NOTE:えへへ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.16,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:661494,663163}Kozue, where are you going?{NOTE:こずえ。どこへ行くんです？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:05.20,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:664289,665206}To study.{NOTE:勉強よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:22.09,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:679888,682098}Is Kozue still up?{NOTE:こずえ未だ起きているのかな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:24.85,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:682098,684851}Yes. I brought her tea a while ago.{NOTE:え。さっきお茶を持ってったんですけど。}
