Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:12:01.47,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:715924,721471}But it was always her dream to enter\NFujimi High School and play volleyball there.{NOTE:富士見高校へ進学してバレーをするのがあの子の以前からの希望ですものね。}
