Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:27.15,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:863279,867158}But don't tell your parents about my pops' illness.{NOTE:でもおじさんおばさんには親父の病気のこと内緒だぜ。}
