Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:53.60,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:890139,893601}I'd like to see your notes while I'm absent from school.{NOTE:僕が学校休んでる間授業のノートを見せてもらいたいんだけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:54.22,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:893601,894227}What do you think?{NOTE:どうかな？}
