Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:19.41,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:915456,919419}But I don't want to abandon the rookies until their tournament no matter what.{NOTE:でも新人戦が始まるまでどうしてもバレーの練習をやめたくないのよ。}
