Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:52.95,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:947155,952952}I'll work hard so that I can enter Fujimi High School and continue studying and playing volleyball.{NOTE:私も富士見高校に入って大いに勉強し、大いにバレーができるよう頑張るわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:57.03,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:952952,957039}We'll crush any obstacles with our will power.{NOTE:どんな苦しみにも若い力を思いっ切りぶつけて。}
