Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:29.52,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105938,1109525}Those are the eyes of someone who is set on achieving their goal.{NOTE:あれは何がに全力を挙げてぶつかっていけるものだけは持っている素晴らしい目だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:35.65,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111694,1115656}You're feeling lonely because Kozue gets further and further away from us.{NOTE:ママはこの間こずえが離れていくみたいで寂しいと言うだが。}
